              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Minyon</span></p><p>Son aşama 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Elektrik Hasarı </span>verir, aktif karakterine<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> \"Karga Tüyünün Himayesi\" </span>uygular.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Karga Tüyünün Himayesi</span></strong></p><p>Eklenen karakterin<span style=\"color: rgb(155, 156, 159)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Element Becerisi</span><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 156, 159)\"> </span>ve<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Element Patlaması</span><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 156, 159)\"> </span>fazladan 1 Hasar verir.</p><p>Kullanım Hakkı: 2</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/27/25073864/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7438001199469602173.png",
